		<aside>
			<title>For Reflection</title> 
			<p>
				Suppose that you are looking at a function of linear cost.  Can you come up with a formula if you are given only a <m>C(x)</m> graph? Why or why not? What if you are given only a <m>\Delta C</m> graph? Why or why not?
			</p>
